>
>    https://github.com/agl/pond

See also http://dee.su/cables, already included as a component in
Liberti Linux.  It's essentially a peer-to-peer mail proxy between Tor
hidden services; almost a 2012 take on the old UUCP bang paths, by the
look of it.

